<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Hugh Jackman and wife Deborra-Lee Furness stepped out for a walk in New York City on Tuesday. </p>

<p>The pair put safety first as they wore face masks while strolling with their dogs, Dali and Allegra. </p>

<p>Wolverine actor Hugh, 51, and his actress wife, 64, were both dressed casually for the walk and chatted happily during the outing. </p>

<p>Stroll: Hugh Jackman and wife Deborra-Lee Furness stepped out for a walk in New York City on Tuesday. Both pictured </p>

<p>Hugh opted for a pale surgical mask, wore with a blue t-shirt and a grey sweatshirt over the top. </p>

<p>He added a pair of grey track pants to the ensemble, and black sneakers worn without socks. </p>

<p>The star had on a black baseball cap with an emblem on the front, and had his glasses tucked into the neckline of his top. </p>

<p>Puppy power: The pair put safety first as they wore face masks while strolling with their dogs, Dali and Allegra</p>

<p>Nice day for it: Wolverine actor Hugh, 51, and his actress wife, 64, were both dressed casually for the walk and chatted happily during the outing</p>

<p>Deborra-Lee wore a black hoodie with a white graphic design, and a pair of dark workout tights. </p>

<p>She added a black and white face mask to her ensemble, and had on a pair of red sneakers. </p>

<p>Her blonde hair was up in a loose ponytail, with curls around her face, and appeared to be makeup free.      </p>

<p>Play time: Deborra-Lee wore a black hoodie with a white graphic design, and a pair of dark workout tights. She stopped to play with her pup as she walked </p>

<p>Hugh recently returned from a a family holiday in the Hamptons with his wife and their two children. </p>

<p>In July, The Greatest Showman actor revealed he was homesick for Australia after a lengthy lockdown in New York City due to the coronavirus pandemic.</p>

<p>Deborra-Lee and the couple's children had initially been in Melbourne when COVID-19 was declared a pandemic in March.</p>

<p>But they returned to the U.S. just four days later in order to keep the family together.</p>

